name: Appreciate You 093
description:
This token gives you access to a five minute performance on December 31, 2021, in which we meet over Zoom, and I appreciate you. At your session time, you can enter by clicking the link that will appear in the view above.

You may hold or transfer this token before or after the performance, as you’d like. If you transfer this token, you must spend five minutes appreciating the new owner.

Performance will begin promptly. Please be ready with Zoom installed and wallet handy to verify token ownership.
